*** archived ***

this repo served its purpose but is superseded by yurapyon/mini

===

untyped

forth in zig (and someday webassembly)

goals:
  - remain true to core principles of forth
    - simplicity
    - directness
  - usable as a general purpose language on linux
  - embeddable
  - enable hot reloading

features:
  - takes some features from ansi forth and gforth
  - direct-threaded
  - floats
  - files
  - dictionaries
    - kindof like wordlists
    - useful for hot reloading
  - coroutines

planned:
  - webassembly
  - error reporting / stack traces
  - terminal drawing
  - usable as a shell
  - dynamic loading of object files to extend functionality

MIT
